{"tid":2125614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"抗衡中國！ 英國擬全面改革《叛國法》 效忠外國將被定罪","createTime":"2020-07-26T09:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T05:41:31.000Z","uid":227801,"like":254,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"6f2315aa205b07c36d6db3c1eeba33d794ac24d8","tid":2125614,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:46:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3240293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3240293&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=401e544d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3240293&h=118e145a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3240293</a><br />\n<br />\n2020-07-26 15:43:51<br />\n〔編譯陳成良／綜合報導〕英國《星期日郵報》25日報導，為抗衡來自中國與俄羅斯的威脅，首相強森（Boris Johnson）將引入全新的《叛國法》和《間諜法》，並重修《官方保密法》，藉以修補、防堵當前法律漏洞。強森希望能在未來幾個月成為正式法律，這是自1695年，即325年來最大規模修改叛國法律的行動，也將使英國與美國、澳洲等盟友立場一致。<br />\n英國正在華為問題上跟中國陷入對峙，7月初一份情報指控，中國企圖通過操縱英國精英人物來支持華為，這個消息在英國政界引起震動，也讓兩國關於華為的外交戰發生轉折。<br />\n<br />\n《星期日郵報》報導引述唐寧街消息人士稱，英國政府正在擬定的「三面夾擊」方。新的叛國法將規定，宣誓效忠外國勢力或組織的人，若試圖進入英國、在境內活動，將被定罪。<br />\n此外，新的反間諜法將造冊記錄具有影響力的外國特務或代理人，並針對英國銀行家、律師與服務供應商採取更嚴格的管制，試圖壓制協助外國敵人的公民。此外，也將重修《官方保密法案》，以切合現今數位時代的需要。<br />\n報導中說，英國府希望藉著這些行動，讓相關法律更加完善，為英國的情報和國安機構提供支援，也讓英國在這方面與其他盟國包括美國和澳洲看齊。"},{"pid":"a389fdf98ff8b0d99be6cbf896c635625144f83f","tid":2125614,"uid":227801,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:47:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539910-20200726.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539910-20200726.htm&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=e145dabf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539910-20200726.htm&h=a43bd8e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539910-20200726.htm</a><br />\n英國國防大臣華禮仕表示，英國政府正重新審視外交、安全及國防政策，將會大幅提升應對來自俄羅斯及中國在太空領域的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n華禮仕在《星期日電訊報》表示，俄羅斯在原本屬於和平領域的太空，試驗具有武器特性的衛星，而中國亦正發展具攻擊性的太空武器，威脅國家安全，兩國的行為令英國要重新審視國家安全法律。<br />\n<br />\n另外，英國《星期日郵報》引述唐寧街消息人士報道，因應來自俄羅斯和中國的威脅，首相約翰遜計劃大幅修改《反叛國法》，包括修訂跟踪外國特工的間諜法和重寫《官方機密法》，以配合數碼時代，報道表示，今次是自叛國法律在1695年以來的最大修改。"},{"pid":"f59cdbe1752fe450a3f4f95f58b2b62a1ff8bd64","tid":2125614,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:48:23.000Z","msg":"正啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed462d5644a54fe8cd88091e7cc9c810c2388f60","tid":2125614,"uid":210140,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:48:25.000Z","msg":"藍絲：咁你班友又反香港國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b3be58fb6d660d41fff68d6dcb5fc08e5472bb","tid":2125614,"uid":79410,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:49:01.000Z","msg":"721 白衣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e606d487a49b85a7c1258c77dd5ec155c9ebfcc","tid":2125614,"uid":25409,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"公務員宣誓之後再去英國會唔會中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809ab512849fd17944d975fa23eaf46d67b91655","tid":2125614,"uid":154486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:51:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8560187/Boris-Johnson-set-Britains-treason-laws-biggest-shakeup-1695.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-8560187%2FBoris-Johnson-set-Britains-treason-laws-biggest-shakeup-1695.html&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=6e617f31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8560187/Boris-Johnson-set-Britains-treason-laws-biggest-shakeup-1695.html</a><br />\